n-chi b´et ttxlaj a´. Qa at jun xjal n-chi ẍch´in, b´a´n t-xi kyq´o´n txqantl toj
tze´ twitz ky-wi´, aye ẍplon tzqij n-chi b´aj ky-xu´n kyi´j aye n-chi okx.

