t-xu´k t-xu´k t-xe´chil t-xe´l ky-q´ob´, extzen aye t-xu´k n-chi kyaj kyq´o´n jun ky-b´i´n te jumajx toj tzqij. A
ax ikx ok tka´yin yek´b´il qa noq jun otoq tz´el tpa´n tib´. Xi tq´o´n chjonte kye oxlaj txuk.


