Compys, xi t-ximin tuk´e jun t-xob´il.

Scavengers.

Aye compys mya n-chi ky-ka´yin junjen nya b´a´n. Chʼixmi ik kyten ik tzeʼn qe ẍneʼl, ex e jaw weʼ
extzen t-xe´l tuk´e junjun tal t-xob´il, tze´nku aye q´a. Extzun b´i´n twitz qa at ky-veneno. A ky-chib´jel
attoq jun veneno nya nim in bʼant tuʼn aju in najbʼen kyuʼn tuʼn kykubʼ kybʼyoʼn txkup mintiʼ kyxbʼalun.

Aye txuk mya b´a´n ky-b´is, chi t-xim, n-chi tzaj t-xob´il.

A tnejel kyxol aye compys n-chi kub´ qe´ twi witz, n-chi ka´yin ti´j. Kubʼ ten junlo jweʼ metro t-xeʼ,
twitz t-xilen, extzen noq n-ka´yin ti´j. Atzun junjuntl e kuʼtz toj chʼin ambʼil, ex e kubʼ weʼ toj jun txol.
N-ka´yin. N-chi ẍch´in kyib´aj extzen n-chi ẍch´in extzen n-chi ẍch´in ky-q´ob´ ky-q´ob´.

